WEBVTT

01:00:40.360 --> 01:00:41.200
Please listen to me.

01:00:41.760 --> 01:00:43.920
We came here in
2012 from Sri Lanka

01:00:44.040 --> 01:00:45.080
We were at the
Mandapam Refugee camp

01:00:45.160 --> 01:00:46.800
We have been here after that.

01:00:46.880 --> 01:00:49.160
Why should we trust
what you say?

01:00:49.280 --> 01:00:50.560
Please trust me. I live here.
